data.description: Stunning 6-Bedroom Single Family Home in Stone Ridge Subdivision Welcome to this exquisite family home with a fully finished basement nestled in the desirable Stone Ridge Subdivision. This property boasts a variety of unique features that are sure to impress. As you step inside, you are captivated by a beautifully designed craftsman custom built home.  Custom ceilings throughout the home. A beautiful kitchen featuring granite countertops, custom cabinets, and high-end appliances. This chef's dream kitchen includes a built-in gas range, perfect for culinary enthusiasts and entertaining guests. Situated on a fully fenced acre lot, this property offers an abundance of outdoor space, including a covered patio ideal for al fresco dining and a dedicated RV parking area. The fully finished basement provides additional living space, perfect for a home theater, game room, or guest suite. The mature landscaping adds the perfect touch of tranquility to this already captivating property.
